Description: # Any Ascii
        [![JitPack](https://jitpack.io/v/com.hunterwb/any-ascii.svg)](https://jitpack.io/#com.hunterwb/any-ascii)
        
        Unicode to ASCII transliteration
        
        #### Table of Contents
        
        - [Glossary](#glossary)
        - [Java](#java)
